#: ../../F/fritterware.rst:5
msgid "fritterware"
msgstr "fritterware"

#: ../../F/fritterware.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../F/fritterware.rst:9
msgid ""
"An excess of capability that serves no productive end. The canonical example"
" is font-diddling software on the Mac (see :ref:`macdink`\\); the term "
"describes anything that eats huge amounts of time for quite marginal gains "
"in function but seduces people into using it anyway. See also :ref:`window-"
"shopping`\\."
msgstr ""
"生産的な目的に役立たない過剰な機能。典型的な例はMacのフォントいじりソフトウェア(:ref:`macdink`\\ "
"を参照)。この用語は、ごくわずかな機能向上のために膨大な時間を食うが、それでも人々を使う気にさせてしまうあらゆるものを表す。\\ "
":ref:`window-shopping`\\ も参照。"
